      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe and Inspector General of Police C.D. A meeting between Mr. Wickramaratne took place at the President's office today (23) afternoon.",
        "This meeting was traditionally held after Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe assumed office as President and Commander-in-Chief, and commemorative gifts were also exchanged."
